540
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:26,920
Brother,

541
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:28,040
it's not your fault.

542
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,640
Before you get here,

543
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:32,520
I've made her angry.

544
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:38,040
Quarrels are common
between young lovers,

545
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:40,080
